to see herself grow old.

1:14:29.032 --> 1:14:31.134
It won't break
like the others.

1:14:31.167 --> 1:14:32.802
I think it's made
out of silver or something.

1:15:35.231 --> 1:15:37.300
Mom!

1:15:50.947 --> 1:15:53.683
Hutch!
Come on! Move!

1:15:53.717 --> 1:15:55.852
Come on, hurry.
Move! Come on, man!

1:15:55.885 --> 1:15:57.787
Move!
Hutch!

1:15:57.821 --> 1:15:59.789
Come on.
Come on, man! Come on!

1:16:04.628 --> 1:16:06.763
Come on!
Come on, Hutch!

1:16:57.180 --> 1:17:00.216
Killer.

1:17:37.987 --> 1:17:40.790
Come to me, clouds.

1:17:40.824 --> 1:17:45.061
May you rise as an evil storm
born to rip them open.

1:17:45.094 --> 1:17:47.797
Let the cover of night
bear witness

1:17:47.831 --> 1:17:49.465
and destroy those who resist

1:17:49.498 --> 1:17:51.901
so they shall harm me not.

1:17:51.935 --> 1:17:54.470
Let the blood
of many cleanse me,

1:17:54.503 --> 1:17:57.540
preserving beauty eternal,

1:17:57.573 --> 1:18:01.010
I pray you.
